                    </div>
                    <span>Disappointing. Technically very good, but overall lacking in originality. Most of these photographs could have been taken by any newspaper sports photographer.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">talent</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
